{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":220,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"今天的菜还不错。","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"派出去巡逻的第一队人，昨天晚上已经……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"这些话等吃完了再说。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"为什么只有在阳光照射到的地方，才有灰尘？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"因为只有在阳光照射到的地方，你才能看得见灰尘，因为你们若看不见那样东西，往往就会认为它根本不存在。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"其实无论你看不看得见，灰尘总是存在的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"世上还有许多别的事也一样，和灰尘一样，它虽然早在你身旁，你却一直看不见它，所以就一直以为它根本不存在。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"幸好阳光总是会照进来的，迟早总是会照进来的……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_hua_man_tian","speaker_name":"花满天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"派出去巡逻的第一队人，大半是我属下，我得去替他们料理后事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":98,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_hua_man_tian","text":"等一等。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_hua_man_tian","speaker_name":"花满天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"堂主还有吩咐？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":104,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_hua_man_tian","text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_hua_man_tian","speaker_name":"花满天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"那等什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":108,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_hua_man_tian","text":"等一个人来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_hua_man_tian","speaker_name":"花满天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"等谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":112,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_hua_man_tian","text":"一个迟早总会来的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_hua_man_tian","speaker_name":"花满天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"他若不来呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"我们就一直等下去好了。","tone":"沉声","chapter":14,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_bai_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"白衣大汉","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"外面有人求见。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_bai_yi_da_han","text":"谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_bai_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"白衣大汉","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"叶开。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_bai_yi_da_han","text":"只有他一个人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_bai_yi_da_han","speaker_name":"白衣大汉","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"只有他一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"他果然来了，来得好快。","tone":"喃喃","chapter":14,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_hua_man_tian","speaker_name":"花满天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"堂主等的就是他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"你们最好就留在这里等我回来。","tone":"沉声","chapter":14,"line_start":146,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"但这次你们却不必一直等下去，因为我一定很快就会回来的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":150,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"好一面大旗，不知道你们是不是天天都将它升上去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"要让这面大旗天天升上去，想必不是件容易事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":196,"line_end":196},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"的确不容易。","tone":"无奈","chapter":14,"line_start":200,"line_end":200},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"不知道世上有没有容易事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只有一样。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":204,"line_end":204},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":206,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"骗自己。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你要骗别人虽很困难，要骗自己却很容易。","tone":"淡然","chapter":14,"line_start":212,"line_end":212}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_bai_yi_da_han","name":"白衣大汉","alias":["大汉","万马堂白衣大汉"],"identity":"万马堂传讯下属","faction":"faction_wan_ma_tang","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"奉命入堂向马空群通报叶开求见的白衣大汉。","personality":{"traits":["恭顺","谨慎","守礼","服从","沉稳"],"speech_style":"简短禀报，称述清楚","temperament":"畏敬堂主、行动利落"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ma_kong_qun","type":"主仆","intensity":45,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"入堂躬身禀报来客"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[14],"source_refs":[{"chapter":14,"line_start":128,"line_end":136,"text":"白衣大汉快步而入，向马空群禀报外面有人求见，并说明来者是叶开。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_ma_kong_qun","updates":{"one_line":"万马堂堂主在危局中以灰尘为喻，暗示自己已看清身边暗伏的背叛。","source_refs":[{"chapter":14,"line_start":34,"line_end":118,"text":"马空群在饭桌上压下巡逻队覆灭的消息，以灰尘之喻警醒云在天、花满天，并等待叶开到来。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_ye_kai","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":14,"line_start":188,"line_end":212,"text":"叶开来到万马堂大旗下，与马空群谈论维持万马堂和自欺之难易。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":221,"line_end":430,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"你呢？你能不能自己骗自己？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":222,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不能。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"所以你日子过得并不愉快。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":226,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这地方死的人已太多了。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":14,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"死的全是不该死的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":246,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"该死的是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"有人认为该死的是我，也有人认为该死的是你，所以……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"所以怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":252,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"所以有人要我来杀你！","tone":"认真","chapter":14,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"有人要你来杀我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":288,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"但你却不想杀我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"你怎么知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为你若想杀我，就不会来告诉我了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":298,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你想必也已看出，要杀我并不是一件容易的事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"你为何不问我，是谁要我来杀你？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我不必问。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":306,"line_end":306},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为我根本就从未将那些人看在眼里。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":14,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"要杀我的人很多，但值得重视的却只有一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我本来也不能断定这人究竟是你，还是傅红雪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"现在你已能断定？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":320,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"其实我本来早就该看出来的。","tone":"沉声","chapter":14,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"你认为那些人全是被傅红雪杀了的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"不是他是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我说过，这地方是我用血汗换来的，绝没有任何人能从我手上抢去。","tone":"沉声","chapter":14,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你知道我有一个女儿吧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":350,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你也认得她？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":356,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"我认得！","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":358,"line_end":358},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你认为她是个怎么样的人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":360,"line_end":360},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"她很好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":362,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你是不是真的很喜欢她？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你一定很奇怪，我为什么要问你这句话？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"我的确有点奇怪。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":14,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我问你，只因我希望你能带她走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"带她走？到哪里去？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":14,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"随便你带她到哪里去，只要是你愿意去的地方，你都可以带她去，这里的东西，无论什么你们都可以带走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"你为什么要我带她走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为……因为我知道她很喜欢你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":388,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"她喜欢我，我们难道就不能留在这里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":390,"line_end":390},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这里马上就有很多事要发生了，我不愿意她也被牵连到里面去，因为她本来就跟这些事全无关系。","tone":"担心","chapter":14,"line_start":392,"line_end":392},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"你的确是个很好的父亲。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":396,"line_end":396},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你答不答应？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":400,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"我说过，这里就是我的家，我既已回来，就不愿再走了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":404,"line_end":404},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你不答应？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":14,"line_start":408,"line_end":408},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"我不能带她走，但却可以保证，无论这里发生了什么事，她都绝不会被牵连进去。","tone":"认真","chapter":14,"line_start":410,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"因为那些事本来就跟她毫无关系。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":414,"line_end":414},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我请你喝杯酒去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":418,"line_end":418}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_ma_kong_qun","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":14,"line_start":242,"line_end":418,"text":"马空群与叶开谈及受命刺杀、傅红雪嫌疑和马芳铃去留，显露守住万马堂与保护女儿的双重心思。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_ye_kai","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"明知叶开受托来杀自己，仍托他保护马芳铃离开是非之地"},{"action":"update","target":"char_ma_fang_ling","type":"亲属","intensity":92,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"预感万马堂将生大变，希望叶开带女儿离开危险"}]},{"id":"char_ye_kai","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":14,"line_start":250,"line_end":410,"text":"叶开向马空群坦白有人要他来杀人，又拒绝带马芳铃离开，承诺不让她受牵连。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_ma_kong_qun","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"坦承刺杀委托却没有立刻动手，与马空群形成试探和互信交织的对峙"}]},{"id":"char_ma_fang_ling","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":14,"line_start":350,"line_end":392,"text":"马空群向叶开询问马芳铃，并希望叶开带她离开即将出事的万马堂。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_ye_kai","type":"恋人","intensity":68,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"马空群指出她喜欢叶开，并想将她托付给叶开带走"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":431,"line_end":700,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_hai_zi","text":"小鬼，是不是又想来偷口酒喝了？","tone":"调侃","chapter":14,"line_start":450,"line_end":450},{"speaker":"char_hai_zi","speaker_name":"孩子","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"你……你为什么要打三姨？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_hai_zi","text":"谁说的？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":14,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_hai_zi","speaker_name":"孩子","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"三姨自己说的，她好像还在爹爹面前告了你一状，你最好小心些。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_hai_zi","text":"三姨呢？","tone":"沉声","chapter":14,"line_start":470,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_hai_zi","speaker_name":"孩子","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"出去了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":472,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_cui_nong","speaker_name":"翠浓","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你不是一直都想看看我的吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":516,"line_end":516},{"speaker":"char_cui_nong","speaker_name":"翠浓","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"现在你总算看见我了。","tone":"柔声","chapter":14,"line_start":540,"line_end":540},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"现在我总算看见你了。","tone":"喃喃","chapter":14,"line_start":542,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_cui_nong","speaker_name":"翠浓","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你还没有看够？","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":562,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_cui_nong","speaker_name":"翠浓","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"好，我就让你看个够吧。","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":566,"line_end":566},{"speaker":"char_shen_san_niang","speaker_name":"沈三娘","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"莫忘了我刚才所告诉你的那些话。","tone":"担心","chapter":14,"line_start":572,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_cui_nong","speaker_name":"翠浓","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"我现在让你看，因为情况已变了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":14,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"什么情况变了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":14,"line_start":578,"line_end":578},{"speaker":"char_cui_nong","speaker_name":"翠浓","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"万马堂已经……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":580,"line_end":580},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"闪开！","tone":"厉声","chapter":14,"line_start":590,"line_end":590},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"又是你。","tone":"厉声","chapter":14,"line_start":600,"line_end":600},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"是我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":602,"line_end":602},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"今天我不想杀你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":604,"line_end":604},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"今天我也不想杀你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":606,"line_end":606},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"那么你最好走远些。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":608,"line_end":608},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"我喜欢站在这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":610,"line_end":610},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"难道他是你的女人？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":14,"line_start":612,"line_end":612},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":616,"line_end":616},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"难道你不知道她是个婊子？","tone":"大笑","chapter":14,"line_start":618,"line_end":618},{"speaker":"char_fu_h